{
  "stem": "25651.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Particularly if it's dough, you see, because it squashes as you dive for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you don't see the hand that's throwing it, and you have to watch the window.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And suddenly this thing appears, and you get-- you can't, in fact, gauge the direction.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's the most funny thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I got the hang of it after about three or four.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you sort of get handicapped, because you put pieces of dough inside your shirt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after you have about six or seven of these bits of dough, the whole thing is weighing you down, you see?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you're trying to jump this way and that way to catch them, because he doesn't always throw them the same dir-- direction.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway, some of them got dirty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I picked-- I mean, it was precious stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Picked it all up, brought it to my-- to [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Traute. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't have ovens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had a way of cooking, but not a way of baking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But she sort of cooked it on top of the stove-- the stove, like [INAUDIBLE], you see.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they became rock hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We kids could eat it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was delicious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my mother couldn't eat it, because of her teeth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she always took the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'll eat it later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we all knew that whatever she put into her hand bag, she'd distribute around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once I went with Eve to San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obviously now, after the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we visited a man called-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what's his name?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Karel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in [INAUDIBLE] with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's not one of the Birkenau boys, because he was a bigger boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we all went into his jacuzzi.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
